title: Slaughter Trail (1951) WEB DL XviD
description:

Three outlaws rob the stage and then flee. When their horses give out they murder some Indians to get fresh ones. But this puts the Indians on the war path and they have to take refuge in an Army fort to avoid them

Director: Irving Allen 

Stars: Brian Donlevy, Gig Young, Virginia Grey
